query:
SELECT DISTINCT lm.subjectId, lm.userId, s.name as subjectName, COUNT(*) as moduleCount
FROM learning_modules lm
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON lm.subjectId = s.id
GROUP BY lm.subjectId, lm.userId, s.name
LIMIT 20;
